[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "ワルター",
		"romanized_name": "Walther",
		"model_path_hash": "9038662813217487255",
		"text": "ええ、その辺りです。下ろしてください",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_007_038_00123",
		"still_path_hash": "2249055519964613397",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "人造頂獣にお手伝いいただいて、\n工事も順調みたいですね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00124",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "スレイ",
		"romanized_name": "Slade",
		"model_path_hash": "1119361770767559406",
		"text": "ええ。人造頂獣の導入当初は不安や反発もありましたが",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_209_038_00125",
		"still_path_hash": "5581277904703418049",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "錬金党が悪さに使ったもんね……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_038_00126",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "リアス",
		"romanized_name": "Rias",
		"model_path_hash": "8538886338969864227",
		"text": "でも、人造頂獣が悪いわけじゃなくて\n使った人が悪かったんだよね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_208_038_00127",
		"still_path_hash": "1321279492992502345",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "スレイ",
		"romanized_name": "Slade",
		"model_path_hash": "1119361770767559406",
		"text": "それに加えて、人間の仕事を取られるんじゃないか……\nそういう不安もあったようだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_209_038_00128",
		"still_path_hash": "5581277904703418049",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "スレイ",
		"romanized_name": "Slade",
		"model_path_hash": "1119361770767559406",
		"text": "人造頂獣は力仕事に向いているが、仕上げといった\n細かい仕事は向いていないから、それも杞憂だったな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_209_038_00129",
		"still_path_hash": "5581277904703418049",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "近くの人たちも、人造頂獣の仕事ぶりを\n見に来てくれているみたいですね？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00130",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "おっきなものを動かすのは、見てて気持ちいいよね。\nゴゴンガ、力持ちだ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_038_00131",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "ゴゴンガ？\nあの人造頂獣の名前だっけ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00132",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "リアス",
		"romanized_name": "Rias",
		"model_path_hash": "8538886338969864227",
		"text": "そうそう、レスナちゃんも呼んでみて！\n頑張れー、ゴゴンガーって",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_208_038_00133",
		"still_path_hash": "1321279492992502345",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "ご、ゴゴンガー……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00134",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "リアス",
		"romanized_name": "Rias",
		"model_path_hash": "8538886338969864227",
		"text": "声が小さい、もっと大きな声で！\nもう１回、せーのっ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_208_038_00135",
		"still_path_hash": "1321279492992502345",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "頑張れ、ゴゴンガ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00136",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "あっ……えへへ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00137",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "レスナちゃん、気付いてもらえてよかったね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_038_00138",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "うん。人造頂獣も、\nこんな風に受け入れてもらえてよかった",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00139",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "リアス",
		"romanized_name": "Rias",
		"model_path_hash": "8538886338969864227",
		"text": "うんうん、レスナちゃんたちのおかげだね！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_208_038_00140",
		"still_path_hash": "1321279492992502345",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "私たちの……？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00141",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "スレイ",
		"romanized_name": "Slade",
		"model_path_hash": "1119361770767559406",
		"text": "大陸中で、レスナさんたち錬金術士が活躍していた\nことは話題になっていますから",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_209_038_00142",
		"still_path_hash": "5581277904703418049",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "リアス",
		"romanized_name": "Rias",
		"model_path_hash": "8538886338969864227",
		"text": "錬金術を知らなかった人も、分からないからって\n怖がっていた人も、錬金術のすごさを知り始めて――",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_208_038_00143",
		"still_path_hash": "1321279492992502345",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "リアス",
		"romanized_name": "Rias",
		"model_path_hash": "8538886338969864227",
		"text": "ランターナ中で、\n錬金術が受け入れられてきたんだよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_208_038_00144",
		"still_path_hash": "1321279492992502345",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "スレイ",
		"romanized_name": "Slade",
		"model_path_hash": "1119361770767559406",
		"text": "錬金術と一緒に人造頂獣も話題になって、\nその便利さとかが注目されているみたいです",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_209_038_00145",
		"still_path_hash": "5581277904703418049",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "スレイ",
		"romanized_name": "Slade",
		"model_path_hash": "1119361770767559406",
		"text": "今や、錬金術があれば何ができるのか\n期待している人も多いですからね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_209_038_00146",
		"still_path_hash": "5581277904703418049",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "そうなんだね……嬉しいな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00147",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "……実際に人造頂獣の被害にあった州では、\nここまですんなり受け入れられはしないだろうけど――",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00148",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "スレイ",
		"romanized_name": "Slade",
		"model_path_hash": "1119361770767559406",
		"text": "人造頂獣は決して危険な存在というだけではない……\nいつか分かってもらえるんじゃないでしょうか",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_209_038_00149",
		"still_path_hash": "5581277904703418049",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "リアス",
		"romanized_name": "Rias",
		"model_path_hash": "8538886338969864227",
		"text": "ハルフェンを復興するのにも、\nゴゴンガの力がとっても助かったもんね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_208_038_00150",
		"still_path_hash": "1321279492992502345",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "リアス",
		"romanized_name": "Rias",
		"model_path_hash": "8538886338969864227",
		"text": "ゴゴンガー！　いつもありがとー！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_208_038_00151",
		"still_path_hash": "1321279492992502345",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "スレイ",
		"romanized_name": "Slade",
		"model_path_hash": "1119361770767559406",
		"text": "ところで……レスナさんたちがここまで来たのは\n人造頂獣の様子を見に来ただけじゃないですよね？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_209_038_00152",
		"still_path_hash": "5581277904703418049",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "あ、うん……実はいよいよ果ての大陸へ向かう準備が\n整ったんだ。出かける前に挨拶しようと思って",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00153",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "リアス",
		"romanized_name": "Rias",
		"model_path_hash": "8538886338969864227",
		"text": "果ての大陸……そこにはたくさんのマナが\n眠ってるんだよね？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_208_038_00154",
		"still_path_hash": "1321279492992502345",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "スレイ",
		"romanized_name": "Slade",
		"model_path_hash": "1119361770767559406",
		"text": "それを持ち帰ることができれば、俺たちのアトリエも\nまた動き出すかもしれない……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_209_038_00155",
		"still_path_hash": "5581277904703418049",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "リアス",
		"romanized_name": "Rias",
		"model_path_hash": "8538886338969864227",
		"text": "うん！　だからってわけじゃないけど\nレスナちゃんたちの冒険が上手くいくように祈ってる！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_208_038_00156",
		"still_path_hash": "1321279492992502345",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 34,
		"localized_name": "リアス",
		"romanized_name": "Rias",
		"model_path_hash": "8538886338969864227",
		"text": "っていうか、ぶっちゃけ一緒に行きたいんだけど……\nまだ、先にしなきゃならないことがあるんだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_208_038_00157",
		"still_path_hash": "1321279492992502345",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 35,
		"localized_name": "スレイ",
		"romanized_name": "Slade",
		"model_path_hash": "1119361770767559406",
		"text": "ハルフェンは無事に復興できました。\n次は町の礎となった祖先の魂を救いたいんです",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_209_038_00158",
		"still_path_hash": "5581277904703418049",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 36,
		"localized_name": "リアス",
		"romanized_name": "Rias",
		"model_path_hash": "8538886338969864227",
		"text": "おじいちゃんとまた一緒に店をやる……\nそう、約束したからね！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_208_038_00159",
		"still_path_hash": "1321279492992502345",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 37,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "うん……リアスちゃんにはリアスちゃんの目的がある。\nその目的が、叶うといいなって私も思うよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00160",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 38,
		"localized_name": "リアス",
		"romanized_name": "Rias",
		"model_path_hash": "8538886338969864227",
		"text": "ありがとう！　まずはまだ行ってない街とか島……\nあと異邦人の先輩に相談してみようと思ってるんだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_208_038_00161",
		"still_path_hash": "1321279492992502345",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 39,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "うん、それは名案だよ！　世界は広いし、\n別の世界の知恵もあれば、きっと解決策が見つかるよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00162",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 40,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "お互いに、頑張ろうねっ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_038_00163",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 41,
		"localized_name": "スレイ",
		"romanized_name": "Slade",
		"model_path_hash": "1119361770767559406",
		"text": "はい！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_209_038_00164",
		"still_path_hash": "5581277904703418049",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]